## Accessibility Requirements
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance for medical interfaces
- High contrast ratios for critical medical information
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader optimization for medical data
- Professional medical iconography

## Medical UI Components
- Clean card-based layouts with subtle shadows
- Patient case cards with status indicators
- AI agent visualization cards
- Real-time data cards with progress indicators
- Multi-step form progress indicators for medical workflows

## Responsive Design
- Seamless experience across devices for healthcare professionals
- Tablet-optimized interfaces for medical dashboards
- Mobile-friendly patient communication interfaces
- Proper scaling for medical data visualization